{"tid":1545521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"主權問題大陸最驚, 明唔明呀, 侵侵幫左手要玩大D先得嫁","createTime":"2019-09-06T02:48:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T02:01:44.000Z","uid":285855,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"2b68a4413c8e2295a0b4d4063ec7f94fef4a6798","tid":1545521,"uid":285855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:48:29.000Z","msg":"侵侵叫大陸還清債單野<br />\n我地香港人要攪大佢先得嫁<br />\n自己都唔講有乜用<br />\n因為如果成立香港唔理係邊個都一定唔會係中共<br />\n中國4個自貿區全部<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">收能晒皮根本攪唔起</span></strong><br />\n宜家都仲唔可以無左香港<br />\n佢地D自貿區D外國公司已經全部撤晒<br />\n所以點解一直講主權<br />\n之前一直唔多理侵侵上月尾問大陸還清債後<br />\n大陸快左咁多其中一個原因<br />\n如果香港無問題無事發生<br />\n就唔改變主權, 現狀BABABA<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">主權</span>    <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">主權</span>     <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">主權</span> </strong>呀<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中共無香港主權呀</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nP牌一日得一PO, 幫手推推啦大家"},{"pid":"33aa5d32adb57c32fda21c8dfe64e306a2571e0c","tid":1545521,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:49:07.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f9f9c15d82cfc65c830393fd9e29599620b92b1","tid":1545521,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:51:24.000Z","msg":"全港連儂牆要人，文宣要人！<br />\n<br />\n8/9 美領事館 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>衛城長久戰，全民都抗爭；<br />\n拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗；</strong><br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制支持「邪惡」「無良」的商店，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點吶喊！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一個post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests #Chinazi<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84HxD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=8fa7800b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.06"},{"pid":"21e38a685f64c7e2004e099602d43de6f690192a","tid":1545521,"uid":236281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4uDunN2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4uDunN2.jpg&h=e2997a88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MxR0us2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMxR0us2.jpg&h=a586f6d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8cb500b3e4f72fca13e058ed572e816693675552","tid":1545521,"uid":285855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:57:06.000Z","msg":"自貿區唔成功<br />\n中共未可以無香港<br />\n侵侵見到中共無左香港<br />\n絕對樂見其成<br />\n就算幫唔到自己<br />\n都可以減弱人地<br />\n我地要識要拎埋呢D point先得"},{"pid":"0e6949f746a904380033d2beac0b4ae4369611c7","tid":1545521,"uid":158235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:59:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d6fee0ab938c8bf5c318939